title.rendered: Day 4. GSaints Swimwear – Miami Swim Week

content.rendered:
Miami Swim Week Powered by Art Hearts Fashion Day 4. 

24Fashion TV Exclusive: 

GSaints Swimwear

GSaints Swimwear followed, with standout silhouettes in an original collection debuting bold hues and exotic prints.

GSaints Swimwear takes its wearers to the relaxed ease of an island beach. Each season, we take on a clean look with silhouettes that throwback to classic cuts and bold hues. Our unique styles and exotic prints stand out on the beach without competing with it. Each piece is flecked with unique elements signature to the GSaints brand. To us, fashion should favor utility and comfort, but it better look damn good while doing it! Designer: Tracey Saintil

Instagram: @gsaintsgirls Facebook: GSaints Swimwear Twitter: @gsaintsswim https://www.gsaintsapparel.com/

Photo by Natalie Svors. Exclusively for 24Fashion TV.
